===Etymology===
From {{compound|grape|fruit}}, an allusion to the grapelike clusters of fruit on the tree.

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|US}} {{IPA|/ˈɡɹeɪp.fɹuːt/}}
*: (as {{term||grape}} + {{term||fruit}}, with stress on {{term||grape}})
*: {{audio|en-us-grapefruit.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===
